						               													<description>DragonStones are the most sought after precious gems in existence. Be the first to gather a set and harness their power!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Each player starts with two stones played on their tower and two cards in hand.&amp;#10;     Player take turns Mining Gems (taking gem stones from a bag) and following the gem specific rules for that particular gem.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Next, the player draws a card and then gets to choose any of the following three actions:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. Play a card  OR&amp;#10;2. Discard a card to mine and stack 2 gems OR&amp;#10;3. Draw another card&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     The final turn begins when one player completes (caps) all six spires; then each other player takes one last turn. Then all players count their points.&amp;#10;     Points are totaled based on number of gems with bonus points for spires that are all single colored or that contain all 5 colored gems!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with the most points wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
